        <date>1931 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The poster features an illustration showing a couple (Charlie Chaplin and Virginia Cherrill) in its centre. The film title in Serbo-Croatian is ‘Svetlost velegrada’ (Light of the big city). The name of the distribution company ‘Makedonija film Skopje’ appears in the bottom right corner.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was released in 1931. Charlie Chaplin was the leading actor, screenwriter and director.</ab>
